        <article class="session-article">
            <h5 class="session-article-head">Criteria for Selection</h5>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        All the proposals will be carefully reviewed by the conference TPC committee and will 
                        be critically analyzed before final selection.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        The person(s) conducting the special session will be entitled as Session/Track chair(s) 
                        for their respective sessions. However, there can be no more than two persons hosting 
                        the session.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Upon selection of the proposal, track chair(s) must furnish the details of the reviewing 
                        committee members (4-5), that will be reviewing the manuscripts.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        For creation of a special session, there must be at least 5 papers registered in the 
                session.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <br>
            </p>
        </article>
        <article class="session-article">
            <h5 class="session-article-head">Role of Track chair(s)</h5>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Track chairs have the responsibility of conducting the manuscript and getting reviews 
                        on them (at least two).
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Track chairs must ensure the quality of submissions as the TPC committee may intervene 
                        and alter the decisions of track chairs in case of a poor quality paper.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Track chairs have to ensure the registration of the selected manuscripts at least 20 
                        days before the conference date.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        All the submissions have to be made in Easy Chair Portal and the track chairs must 
                        keep a track of the paper ids of the submissions.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <br>
            </p>
        </article>
        <article class="session-article">
            <h5 class="session-article-head">Benefits of Track Chair</h5>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Track chairs as token of honor will be given the certificate and memento.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Track chairs will be given a free complementary registration as an author/attendee at the 
                        conference.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Track chairs will be given local hospitality and accommodation at the conference venue.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <br>
            </p>
